EmailTemplate.subject: Invitation to Junior School Information Evening 14 March
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
Thank you for your enquiry regarding potential Year {!Lead.Year_Group__c} {!Lead.Year_of_Entry__c} enrolment.
During the year you will receive invitations to our special events and we would be delighted for you to join us at our Junior School Information Evening on 14 March. It’s a great opportunity to visit our vibrant Junior School, tour our learning spaces and hear first-hand from key Junior School staff and student representatives. You can book directly into the event via our website.
The evening includes an optional tour of the Junior School and a Q&A session with our Head of Junior School, Mrs Rhonda Robson. I have attached an invitation providing further details.
There will also be a supervised Kids Club on the evening. Bookings essential.
If you have any questions at all regarding enrolment or visiting the school, please feel free to contact me and my Enrolments Team via enrolments@sacs.nsw.edu.au.
Kind regards
Bruce Perry Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia direct +61 2 9286 9552 mobile 0404 884 852 email rpedley@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 29286 9550
Catch up with what’s happening at St Andrew’s Cathedral School via Facebook!
You are receiving this invitation as you have previously indicated interest in enrolment at St Andrew’s Cathedral School. We would love you to come to along on our future events however, if you would like to unsubscribe from further invitations, please click here.
